{
  "texts": [
    "Crucially, the module was deployed alongside other optional modules with an emphasis on technology, (business) management or cultural awareness.",
    "Thus it exists in a non-silo configuration where digital capabilities and cultural mediation capabilities are promoted.",
    "The module consists of interrelated thematic units (eleven 2 hour-long classes).",
    "Again, the number of hours and thematic units are presented here as a proposal that other translator trainers can adapt to their needs, i.e.",
    "number of topics, number of hours per topic and even number of practicums."
  ]
}